message.text:
🎥 Bawat Kanto, Bagong Simula: Maligayang Pagdating sa Maynila! 🎬

Sa pagtatapos ng TamHunt 2025, muling nabuo ang mga alaala ng pagkakaisa, kasiyahan, at pakikipagkaibigan. Isa itong paglalakbay na nagbukas ng panibagong kuwento para sa mga Tamaraw na nagnanais tuklasin ang mundo ng pagseserbisyo kasama ang IABF Student Council.

Balikan natin ang mga kaganapan at pakulo na naging bahagi ng makulay na selebrasyon na ito—at hayaan nating muling mabuhay ang kwento sa pamamagitan ng bidyong ito. ✨

#FinestKwentoEveryKanto
#SoaringGreaterHeights

Host: Ace Chezter Sibaro
Director: RB Benito and Heart Nepomuceno
Scriptwriter: Ronn Jasper Repulda and Ace Chezter Sibaro
Videographer: MJ Astilla and Nicole Villa
Editor: Nicole Villa
Caption: Ahzel Uy
Music: Eraserheads - Ligaya

message.text:
🎥 Bawat Kanto, Bagong Simula: Maligayang Pagdating sa Maynila! 🎬

Sa pagtatapos ng TamHunt 2025, muling nabuo ang mga alaala ng pagkakaisa, kasiyahan, at pakikipagkaibigan. Isa itong paglalakbay na nagbukas ng panibagong kuwento para sa mga Tamaraw na nagnanais tuklasin ang mundo ng pagseserbisyo kasama ang IABF Student Council.

Balikan natin ang mga kaganapan at pakulo na naging bahagi ng makulay na selebrasyon na ito—at hayaan nating muling mabuhay ang kwento sa pamamagitan ng bidyong ito. ✨

#FinestKwentoEveryKanto
#SoaringGreaterHeights

message.text:
🎥 Bawat Kanto, Bagong Simula: Maligayang Pagdating sa Maynila! 🎬

Sa pagtatapos ng TamHunt 2025, muling nabuo ang mga alaala ng pagkakaisa, kasiyahan, at pakikipagkaibigan. Isa itong paglalakbay na nagbukas ng panibagong kuwento para sa mga Tamaraw na nagnanais tuklasin ang mundo ng pagseserbisyo kasama ang IABF Student Council.

Balikan natin ang mga kaganapan at pakulo na naging bahagi ng makulay na selebrasyon na ito—at hayaan nating muling mabuhay ang kwento sa pamamagitan ng bidyong ito. ✨

#FinestKwentoEveryKanto
#SoaringGreaterHeights

Host: Ace Chezter Sibaro
Director: RB Benito and Heart Nepomuceno
Scriptwriter: Ronn Jasper Repulda and Ace Chezter Sibaro
Videographer: MJ Astilla and Nicole Villa
Editor: Nicole Villa
Caption: Ahzel Uy
Music: Eraserheads - Ligaya

message.text:
🎥 Bawat Kanto, Bagong Simula: Maligayang Pagdating sa Maynila! 🎬

Sa pagtatapos ng TamHunt 2025, muling nabuo ang mga alaala ng pagkakaisa, kasiyahan, at pakikipagkaibigan. Isa itong paglalakbay na nagbukas ng panibagong kuwento para sa mga Tamaraw na nagnanais tuklasin ang mundo ng pagseserbisyo kasama ang IABF Student Council.

Balikan natin ang mga kaganapan at pakulo na naging bahagi ng makulay na selebrasyon na ito—at hayaan nating muling mabuhay ang kwento sa pamamagitan ng bidyong ito. ✨

#FinestKwentoEveryKanto
#SoaringGreaterHeights

Host: Ace Chezter Sibaro
Director: RB Benito and Heart Nepomuceno
Scriptwriter: Ronn Jasper Repulda and Ace Chezter Sibaro
Videographer: MJ Astilla and Nicole Villa
Editor: Nicole Villa
Caption: Ahzel Uy
Music: Eraserheads - Ligaya

message.text:
🎥 Bawat Kanto, Bagong Simula: Maligayang Pagdating sa Maynila! 🎬

Sa pagtatapos ng TamHunt 2025, muling nabuo ang mga alaala ng pagkakaisa, kasiyahan, at pakikipagkaibigan. Isa itong paglalakbay na nagbukas ng panibagong kuwento para sa mga Tamaraw na nagnanais tuklasin ang mundo ng pagseserbisyo kasama ang IABF Student Council.

Balikan natin ang mga kaganapan at pakulo na naging bahagi ng makulay na selebrasyon na ito—at hayaan nating muling mabuhay ang kwento sa pamamagitan ng bidyong ito. ✨

#FinestKwentoEveryKanto
#SoaringGreaterHeights

message.text:
#IABFAdvisory
 
Re: E-Book Access for First Semester S.Y. 2025-2026

Attention, IABF!

For those utilizing E-Books as part of your course requirements, please take note of the following important reminders:
 
This semester, Digital Solutions (DS) access codes are obtained by signing the Student Undertaking form, with fees charged directly to your student account.

The corresponding amount appears in the Statement of Account within 1–2 months after receiving the access codes (Cengage and Pearson) or after account activation (McGraw-Hill).

Access codes are released daily, subject to stock availability. Requests submitted after 6:00 PM are processed the next business day.
 
Kindly scan the QR code or check the following links below:
 
CENGAGE
⁦https://bit.ly/CengageSU⁩
 
PEARSON
⁦https://bit.ly/PearsonSU⁩
 
MCGRAW-HILL
https://bit.ly/McgrawhillSU⁩  
 
Thank you for your cooperation.
 
Souce: Business Administration Department
 
#SoaringGreaterHeights
 
Pubmat by Yesha Eugenio and Alyanna Madrideo

#IABFAdvisory
 
Re: E-Book Access for First Semester S.Y. 2025-2026

Attention, IABF!

For those utilizing E-Books as part of your course requirements, please take note of the following important reminders:
 
This semester, Digital Solutions (DS) access codes are obtained by signing the Student Undertaking form, with fees charged directly to your student account.

The corresponding amount appears in the Statement of Account within 1–2 months after receiving the access codes (Cengage and Pearson) or after account activation (McGraw-Hill).

Access codes are released daily, subject to stock availability. Requests submitted after 6:00 PM are processed the next business day.
 
Kindly scan the QR code or check the following links below:
 
CENGAGE
⁦https://bit.ly/CengageSU⁩
 
PEARSON
⁦https://bit.ly/PearsonSU⁩
 
MCGRAW-HILL
https://bit.ly/McgrawhillSU⁩  
 
Thank you for your cooperation.
 
Souce: Business Administration Department
 
#SoaringGreaterHeights
 
Pubmat by Yesha Eugenio and Alyanna Madrideo

message.text:
#IABFAdvisory
 
Re: E-Book Access for First Semester S.Y. 2025-2026

Attention, IABF!

For those utilizing E-Books as part of your course requirements, please take note of the following important reminders:
 
This semester, Digital Solutions (DS) access codes are obtained by signing the Student Undertaking form, with fees charged directly to your student account.

The corresponding amount appears in the Statement of Account within 1–2 months after receiving the access codes (Cengage and Pearson) or after account activation (McGraw-Hill).

Access codes are released daily, subject to stock availability. Requests submitted after 6:00 PM are processed the next business day.
 
Kindly scan the QR code or check the following links below:
 
CENGAGE
⁦https://bit.ly/CengageSU⁩
 
PEARSON
⁦https://bit.ly/PearsonSU⁩
 
MCGRAW-HILL
https://bit.ly/McgrawhillSU⁩  
 
Thank you for your cooperation.
 
Souce: Business Administration Department
 
#SoaringGreaterHeights
 
Pubmat by Yesha Eugenio and Alyanna Madrideo
